name: Crisis existencial | Existencial Crisis
description: This is my face and this is my story: a queer woman that escaped from her toxic family and enviroment at 19 years old. Actually, I'm living alone, trying to figure it out what to do with my life. I have a lot of trauma and sadness in my eyes and it shows. But I remember that old-self, that angy and sad teenager that used to feel alone and misunderstood. I have to keep going for her. I need to honor her and her dreams.
